{%- style -%}
  .medvi-faq {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #fff;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #121231;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e4dcd8;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__question h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #121231;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__icon {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__icon::before,
  .medvi-faq__icon::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    background: #121231;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__icon::before {
    width: 2px;
    height: 16px;
    top: 4px;
    left: 11px;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__icon::after {
    width: 16px;
    height: 2px;
    top: 11px;
    left: 4px;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__answer {
    display: none;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__item.active .medvi-faq__answer {
    display: block;
  }
  
  .medvi-faq__item.active .medvi-faq__icon::before {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }
{%- endstyle -%}

<div class="medvi-faq" id="faq">
  <div class="medvi-faq__container">
    <div class="medvi-faq__header">
      <h2 class="medvi-faq__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="medvi-faq__list">
      <div class="medvi-faq__item">
        <div class="medvi-faq__question">
          <h3>How much does the program cost?</h3>
          <div class="medvi-faq__icon"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="medvi-faq__answer">
          <p>The MEDVi Semaglutide program starts at $179 for your first month with no contract. This cost covers your physician review, full personalized plan, 1:1 guidance, metabolic report, and the cost of the prescription medication shipped right to your door. Refills are locked in at $299 and include all the same program benefits.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="medvi-faq__item">
        <div class="medvi-faq__question">
          <h3>Will this work for me?</h3>
          <div class="medvi-faq__icon"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="medvi-faq__answer">
          <p>Our providers will explore prescribing compounded GLP-1 medications for you, if appropriate - with effective, GLP-1 ingredients. Compounded medication can provide incredible results for you, using active GLP-1 ingredients that help you reach your goals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="medvi-faq__item">
        <div class="medvi-faq__question">
          <h3>What if my insurance doesn't cover the medication?</h3>
          <div class="medvi-faq__icon"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="medvi-faq__answer">
          <p>While all MEDVi prescriptions are cash-pay, your insurance may reimburse you for branded options. We keep compounded medications fairly priced so no insurance is necessary while still working toward your goal weight.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="medvi-faq__item">
        <div class="medvi-faq__question">
          <h3>What can I expect after I sign up?</h3>
          <div class="medvi-faq__icon"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="medvi-faq__answer">
          <p>After you complete your online visit, our medical providers will review your answers and determine whether treatment may be right for you. If appropriate, you will be prescribed medication which will be shipped right from the pharmacy to your door.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.medvi-faq__question').forEach(question => {
    question.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const item = question.closest('.medvi-faq__item');
      item.classList.toggle('active');
    });
  });
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "MEDVi FAQ",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "MEDVi FAQ" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}